1812">Gemeinsame Normdatei</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://id.sbn.it/af/IT\ICCU\RAVV\049838">Service bibliothécaire national</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://id.ndl.go.jp/auth/ndlna/00879967">Bibliothèque nationale de la Diète</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://catalogo.bne.es/uhtbin/authoritybrowse.cgi?action=display&amp;authority_id=XX1015590">Bibliothèque nationale d’Espagne</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://data.bibliotheken.nl/id/thes/p071744290">Bibliothèque royale des Pays-Bas</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://uli.nli.org.il/F/?func=direct&amp;doc_number=000409766&amp;local_base=nlx10">Bibliothèque nationale d’Israël</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://nukat.edu.pl/aut/n%202009153301">Bibliothèque universitaire de Pologne</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://cantic.bnc.cat/registres/CUCId/a11266703">Bibliothèque nationale de Catalogne</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://libris.kb.se/auth/237489">Bibliothèque nationale de Suède</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://viaf.org/processed/BAV%7CADV10295294">Bibliothèque apostolique vaticane</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/canadiana-authorities/index/view?index_name=cdnAutNbr&amp;lang=fr&amp;search_text=0019D7188&amp;page=1&amp;cdnAutNbr0019D7188">Autorités Canadiana</a></span><